description.narrative: Revised project development objective is to improve the availability, quality and efficiency of basic municipal services for the population of the towns which participate in the project. An added objective, as an urgent response to the anticipated floods of the spring of 2012, is to contribute to their mitigation with the supply of emergency materials.
